Take a journey into the future as a schoolgirl with superhuman strength battles a fearsome rival in Central Park Media's remastered release of this breathtaking anime classic. Presented in 1.33:1 full frame and offering seperate English and Japanese audio tracks rendered in Dolby Digital Stereo, this release also offers optional English subtitles. Abundant extra features include trailers and TV spots, an interview with Yuji Moriyama, comic-to-film comparisons, music videos, a look behind the scenes, a fan-art contest, a video restoration documentary, sneak peaks and DVD-ROM content. ~ Jason Buchanan, All Movie Guide
